channel.title: Error on Lin's Editor
channel.description:
Hey, I'm using Lin's interface editor to edit my Game Options Tab on a Delta 317 Non-Renamed client/cache. I'm uploading my new custom sprites into my media using Tom's Cache Editor and saving it, but when I try to edit the interface it's giving me "property value is not valid" and then I can't load my media in the Cache Editor.
Although when I did it with the emote tab, it works.
Any suggestions?
Thank you.
